---
title: Chicken in Bacon and Mushroom Sauce with Garlic Mash and Roasted Carrots
description: A customer favourite, this Chicken in Bacon and Mushroom Sauce is a tried-and-tested recipe that always wins with a crowd.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R339_W09_UK_C3361-19715-10_Main_low-257a8539.jpg
